  I ASKED YOU NOT TO FLY
  SHAUNA'S DAUGHTER OUT HERE,

15:33.566 --> 15:34.666
          BUT YOU DID.

15:35.902 --> 15:37.769
    AND NO ONE WAS
    SUPPOSED TO TELL SHAUNA

15:37.771 --> 15:39.771
       THAT I HAD SEX
       WITH HER DAUGHTER,

15:39.773 --> 15:41.072
          BUT YOU DID.

15:42.042 --> 15:43.574
       MAYBE IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.

15:43.576 --> 15:45.143
     I MEAN, AFTER SHE GETS OVER
     HER INITIAL SHOCK,

15:45.145 --> 15:46.678
    -SHAUNA'S GONNA BE FINE.
    -(door slams)

15:48.081 --> 15:50.882
  JOSH, THESE TWO WEEKS HAVE
  BEEN SOME OF THE BEST TIMES
  I'VE EVER HAD,

15:50.884 --> 15:54.652
  AND I NEVER IMAGINED
  IT WOULD COME TO SUCH
  A HUMILIATING END. GOODBYE!

15:54.654 --> 15:56.120
     SHAUNA, WAIT. (sighs)

15:56.122 --> 15:59.190
       LOOK...
       WE ALL HAVE PASTS.

15:59.192 --> 16:01.225
THE IMPORTANT THING IS
I WANNA BE WITH YOU.

16:01.227 --> 16:04.829
        (emphatically)
        NO, YOU HAD SEX

16:04.831 --> 16:06.764
       WITH MY DAUGHTER!

16:06.766 --> 16:08.833
     WHAT'S THAT THING
     ALL THE AMERICANS SAY?

16:08.835 --> 16:10.702
         OH YEAH. EWW!

16:10.704 --> 16:12.637
       (cellphone beeps)

16:12.639 --> 16:14.205
              OH, IT'S DANIELLE.

16:14.207 --> 16:17.141
    "MOM, MAPLE SYRUP EMERGENCY.
    HAD TO FLY HOME.

16:17.143 --> 16:19.310
      "SO THRILLED
      ABOUT YOU AND JOSH, AND...

16:19.312 --> 16:22.146
"I LOVED SEEING YOU SO HAPPY.
KISS, HUG, DANIELLE."

16:22.148 --> 16:25.249
    (gasps) SEE? SEE?
    SHE CHOSE YOU OVER JOSH.

16:25.251 --> 16:26.918
     I DID THE RIGHT THING.

16:26.920 --> 16:29.654
        I GUESS,
        IN A FUNNY WAY, YOU DID.

16:29.656 --> 16:31.222
                  GOODBYE, GABI.

16:32.625 --> 16:33.858
         GOODBYE, JOSH.

16:35.962 --> 16:40.631
         UH! HUGS ARE
         FOR PEOPLE WHO HAVEN'T
         SLEPT WITH MY DAUGHTER.

16:49.209 --> 16:50.675
                     WHY?

16:51.778 --> 16:53.778
                WHY? WHY?

16:53.780 --> 16:57.081
                  (shouting)
                  WHY? WHY? WHY?

16:57.083 --> 17:00.184
        WHY? WHY, WHY, WHY? WHY?

17:00.186 --> 17:02.820
     WHY? YOU KNOW WHAT?
     DON'T ANSWER THAT QUESTION!

17:02.822 --> 17:03.955
                   GET OUT!

17:06.192 --> 17:07.759
       -(inhales sharply)
       -OUT!

17:18.838 --> 17:21.071
                ¶ ALAN. ¶

17:21.074 --> 17:23.273
               I WOULD SAY,
               "RISE AND SHINE,"

17:23.276 --> 17:25.810
           BUT IT APPEARS
           SOMEBODY ALREADY HAS.

17:26.780 --> 17:28.346
I'M NOT ALAN,

17:28.348 --> 17:30.248
AND THAT'S ONE
OF MY HAIR ROLLERS!

17:30.250 --> 17:33.718
                    AH! YOLANDA!

17:33.720 --> 17:34.886
              YOU WERE SUPPOSED
              TO BE WATCHING ME,

17:34.888 --> 17:37.088
         NOT GETTING
         YOUR WOMAN STINK ON ME.

17:38.324 --> 17:41.192
I'M SORRY!
I CLOSED MY EYES
FOR ONE SECOND,

17:41.194 --> 17:44.829
NEXT THING I KNOW,
I WOKE UP SPOONING
AN ASIAN DANNY DeVITO.

17:46.032 --> 17:48.433
              WAIT, SO YOU SLEPT
              THE WHOLE NIGHT?

17:48.435 --> 17:50.301
               YOU DIDN'T SEE ME
               DO ANYTHING?

17:50.303 --> 17:54.005
OH, RELAX!
WE BOTH SLEPT
THROUGH THE NIGHT.

17:54.007 --> 17:56.040
WHAT'S THE WEIRDEST THING
THAT COULD'VE HAPPENED?
(laughs)

17:59.712 --> 18:02.547
            WAIT.
            HOW DID YOU GET MY--

18:02.549 --> 18:04.148
AND HOW DID YOU
MANAGE TO PUT ON...

18:05.285 --> 18:07.251
        (both screaming)

18:09.355 --> 18:11.389
                (knocks on door)

18:13.293 --> 18:14.425
              (gasps)

18:16.463 --> 18:19.764
      WHY ARE YOU HERE?
      THAT CAN'T BE GOOD.

18:19.766 --> 18:21.265
            GABI, OPEN THE DOOR.

18:25.338 --> 18:28.806
OKAY, FIRST,
LET ME START BY SAYING
I'M REALLY, REALLY SORRY

18:28.808 --> 18:30.908
ABOUT EVERYTHING,
AND TO MAKE IT UP TO YOU,
I MADE YOUR FAVORITE DISH.

18:30.910 --> 18:34.078
  -TRUFFLE MAC AND CHEESE?
  -YOUR SECOND FAVORITE DISH.

18:36.182 --> 18:38.883
    SOFIA CALLED ME,
    AND I KNOW IT WAS YOUR
    MOTHER'S BIRTHDAY THIS WEEK.

18:39.986 --> 18:42.854
   -OH.
   -AND I THINK THAT EXPLAINS
   YOUR BEHAVIOR YESTERDAY.

18:42.856 --> 18:44.822
            NOT EVERY OTHER DAY.

18:46.092 --> 18:48.526
I GUESS THIS TIME
OF YEAR'S REALLY HARD FOR ME.

18:48.528 --> 18:51.195
           I WANT YOU TO KNOW
           MY DOOR'S ALWAYS OPEN
           IF YOU NEED TO TALK.

18:52.198 --> 18:53.798
            NOT MY BEDROOM DOOR.

18:54.868 --> 18:58.836
I GUESS AFTER YOU SAID,
"WHY? WHY? WHY? WHY? WHY?"

18:58.838 --> 19:01.572
IT REALLY
MADE ME THINK, "WHY?"

19:04.144 --> 19:08.045
AND I REALIZED I WAS JUST
TRYING TO LIVE VICARIOUSLY
THROUGH DANIELLE AND SHAUNA.

19:08.047 --> 19:11.315
I THOUGHT MAYBE
IF I COULD GET THEM
BACK TOGETHER, THEN...

19:11.317 --> 19:12.850
        GOD, I WOULD DO
        ANYTHING TO HAVE

19:12.852 --> 19:14.919
     ONE MORE MOMENT
     WITH MY MOM. (crying)

19:14.921 --> 19:15.786
            I KNOW...

19:15.788 --> 19:18.856
  WHICH IS WHY I'M GIVING YOU
  THE REST OF THE WEEK OFF

19:18.858 --> 19:20.424
     AND SENDING YOU
     AND SOFIA ON A LITTLE TRIP.

19:20.426 --> 19:22.260
WHAT? WHERE ARE WE GOING?

19:22.262 --> 19:25.963
    LET ME...
    GIVE YOU A LITTLE HINT.

19:26.866 --> 19:28.966
     JULIA CHILD'S KITCHEN
     IN THE SMITHSONIAN?

19:28.968 --> 19:31.802
    -MY MOM ALWAYS
    WANTED TO TAKE ME HERE.
    -I KNOW.

19:31.804 --> 19:33.838
SOFIA ALREADY PACKED YOUR BAGS.
SHE'S MEETING US AT THE AIRPORT.

19:33.840 --> 19:36.207
  WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.
  I RUINED YOUR RELATIONSHIP,

19:36.209 --> 19:37.441
     AND YOU'RE SENDING ME
     ON A FREE TRIP?

19:37.443 --> 19:38.876
      I SHOULD NOT
      HAVE MENTIONED THAT.

19:40.813 --> 19:43.314
AT LEAST LET ME
GIVE YOU THE CHICKEN PARM
THAT I MADE YOU.

19:43.316 --> 19:46.350
        CHICKEN PARM?
        NOT EVEN TOP 10.

19:48.555 --> 19:50.288
WAIT, WAIT,
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

19:50.290 --> 19:51.989
        ONE MORE THING.

19:53.026 --> 19:54.592
                 (chuckles)

19:54.594 --> 19:55.993
           THANK YOU.

20:07.240 --> 20:09.040
ELLIOT, I HAVE SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU.

20:09.042 --> 20:11.876
 -WHAT?
 -I'VE BEEN HAVING A HARD TIME
 SLEEPING NEXT TO YOU.

20:11.878 --> 20:14.178
I'M SO WORRIED THAT I MIGHT
DO SOMETHING IN MY SLEEP

20:14.180 --> 20:15.446
AND YOU WON'T THINK
I'M SEXY ANYMORE.

20:15.448 --> 20:16.614
            -WHAT?
            -I KNOW.

20:16.616 --> 20:17.882
WITH THIS MONEYMAKER,
THAT'S CRAZY.

20:17.884 --> 20:19.217
BUT WHAT IF?

20:21.354 --> 20:22.853
             YOU'VE BEEN WORRIED
             ABOUT THAT?

20:22.855 --> 20:24.855
           I'VE BEEN WORRIED
           ABOUT THE SAME THING!

20:24.857 --> 20:27.024
OH PLEASE.
YOU DON'T KNOW FROM WORRY.

20:28.461 --> 20:30.962
               I DON'T?
               I WAS SO WORRIED,

20:30.964 --> 20:32.930
              I PAID YOLANDA
              TO WATCH ME SLEEP.

20:32.932 --> 20:35.299
THAT'S SO SWEET!

20:35.301 --> 20:37.134
        -DID YOU DO
        ANYTHING WEIRD?
        -NO.

20:38.071 --> 20:41.005
THIS IS CRAZY.
WHO CARES WHAT
WE DO IN OUR SLEEP?

20:41.007 --> 20:44.008
WE CAN BE OURSELVES.
WE LOVE EACH OTHER.

20:45.445 --> 20:50.114
         -WE DO?
         -WELL... I DO.

20:52.652 --> 20:54.652
          -I DO TOO.
          -(chuckles)

20:57.390 --> 21:00.458
GOOD, BECAUSE I HAVE
SLEEP APNEA.

21:03.997 --> 21:05.663
(muffled)
GOOD NIGHT, SWEETHEART.

21:06.966 --> 21:08.099
                    NIGHT.

21:14.040 --> 21:16.040
           YAY.

21:16.042 --> 21:18.976
(machine hissing)

21:21.948 --> 21:23.914
         OH, WHO CARES?

21:23.916 --> 21:26.083
              YAY.

